<h2 id="6-completion--certification">6. Completion &amp; Certification</h2>

<p><strong>6.1 What are the internship completion criteria?</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>100% attendance</strong> (1 day eligible leave)</li>
  <li>Completion of <strong>MERN development course</strong></li>
  <li>Completion of <strong>assigned project</strong></li>
</ul>

