<h2 id="7-report-submission--deadline">7. Report Submission &amp; Deadline</h2>

<p><strong>7.1 What happens if I miss deadlines?</strong><br />
Late submissions may result in being <strong>flagged as a defaulter</strong>.</p>

<hr />

<h2 id="8-termination--rejoining">8. Termination &amp; Rejoining</h2>

<p><strong>8.1 Can I rejoin after termination due to exams?</strong><br />
No. Any <strong>academic overlap</strong> disqualifies continuation.</p>

<p><strong>8.2 Can I appeal a termination?</strong><br />
No. Terminations are <strong>final</strong>.</p>

<p><strong>8.3 Will future batches be identical?</strong><br />
You must <strong>reapply</strong>. Funding is <strong>not guaranteed</strong>.</p>

