<h2 id="9-vibe-platform">9. ViBe Platform</h2>

<p><strong>9.1 How do I log in to ViBe?</strong><br />
Invite link ‚Üí Continue as Student ‚Üí Continue with Google ‚Üí Dashboard.</p>

<p><strong>9.2 Invite accepted but shows ‚ÄúNo course enrolled‚Äù?</strong><br />
Verify email ‚Üí Check alias ‚Üí Contact Support.</p>

<p><strong>9.3 Why are videos stuck or repeating?</strong><br />
Sequential viewing, camera/mic access, lighting, and noise conditions matter.</p>

<p><strong>9.4 Can I use mobile or tablet?</strong><br />
No. Only <strong>desktop/laptop</strong> is supported.</p>

